{"tid":423861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（情境題）你究竟會點揀","createTime":"2017-10-04T08:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T08:55:30.000Z","uid":136502,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19b4a2c5ab1033b1f9eeaf6e7d76bdb08bfb17a1","tid":423861,"uid":136502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:52:51.000Z","msg":"冇呀 其實好奇咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你結咗婚， 但老婆話你知往後日子都唔俾扑（起碼50年）連摸都唔得摸 睇都唔得睇<br />\n但你又唔得離婚 因為老婆老豆猛料 隨時離婚會連累自己爸媽，做成生命危險<br />\n你又會如何呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：二話不說 過上50年打飛機嘅生活. 係愛呀 哈利！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：緊係謹慎地進行叫雞，搵ptgf，包養小三等等行為啦 on9樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6653d2189ab801251020a21de071cdd03663d052","tid":423861,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"呃負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbfafa154f2ad6aa42391acb062839cb886d96d","tid":423861,"uid":136502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呃負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係想知有幾多人係真愛姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e315948f19470f5cd4e239d21e01c8fd3fec91b","tid":423861,"uid":136502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呃負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係想知有幾多人係真愛姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}